"review_level": "None",
"content": "<h2>Spies were used to collect information, usually of a military nature</h2>\n<p>Joseph's brothers accused of being spies:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:9-Gen42:11\">GEN 42:9–42:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:14-Gen42:16\">GEN 42:14–42:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:30-Gen42:34\">GEN 42:30–42:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num13:1-Num13:20\">NUM 13:1–13:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:32\">NUM 21:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:22\">DEU 1:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:1-Josh2:3\">JOS 2:1–2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:17\">JOS 6:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:22\">JOS 6:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:25\">JOS 6:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:31\">HEB 11:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:25\">JAS 2:25</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:2\">JOS 7:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg1:23-Judg1:24\">JDG 1:23–1:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg18:2\">JDG 18:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg18:14\">JDG 18:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg18:17\">JDG 18:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam10:3\">2SA 10:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr19:3\">1CH 19:3</a></p>\n<h2>Spies were used to incriminate Jesus Christ and the first Christians</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:20-Luke20:22\">LUK 20:20–20:22</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:15-Matt22:16\">MAT 22:15–22:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:13-Mark12:14\">MRK 12:13–12:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:4\">GAL 2:4</a></p>",
